            "product_main_image": "shopify://shop_images/Rogue_Leather_4in_Lever_Belt.jpg",
            "product_rating_description": "<p>Being made of genuine sole leather, this garment is the best lever belt on the list. It features a black suede liner, an embossed Rogue logo, and patented lock-in matte-black lever from nickel-plated steel that replaces a traditional buckle.</p><ul><li><strong>Material: </strong>100% Vegetable Tanned Sole Leather, interior suede liner</li><li><strong>Waist size range: </strong>XS (22”-31”) - XL (39”-48”)</li><li><strong>Width: </strong>4”</li><li><strong>Thickness: </strong>13mm</li><li><strong>Certifications:</strong> IPF Approved</li><li><strong>Warranty: </strong>6 months</li><li><strong>Price: </strong>$$$$$</li></ul>",
            "product_rating_1": "5",
