            "product_main_image": "shopify://shop_images/Gymreapers_10mm_Lever_Belt.jpg",
            "product_rating_description": "<p>Considering the lever belt reviews on the web, this 10mm belt from Gymreapers will be perfect for newbies in lifting. Being made by athletes for athletes, this premium-grade lever belt provides secure support, rigidity, and stability you need during training sessions. Consequently, you'll be able to bring your performance to the next level.</p><ul><li><strong>Material:</strong> leather, interior suede liner</li><li><strong>Waist size range:</strong> XS (24”-31”) - 2XL (39”-46”)</li><li><strong>Width:</strong> 4”</li><li><strong>Thickness: </strong>10 mm</li><li><strong>Certifications: </strong>IPF, IPL, and USAPL approved</li><li><strong>Warranty:</strong> lifetime warranty</li><li><strong>Price:</strong> $$$$</li></ul>",
            "product_rating_1": "5",
