            "second_button_url": "",
            "product_text_content_1": "<p>Gymreapers brand creates sports gear that provides support, stability, and increased performance to push fitness boundaries and become stronger and more endurant.</p><p>The brand's mission is to improve athlete's performance, relieve pain, and add stability to the workout program with durable gear that lasts. Self-improvement is possible through the correctly chosen equipment, which drives athletes to work harder to propel and overcome any limits.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.gymreapers.com/products/10mm-lever-belt-black?aff=172\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.gymreapers.com/products/10mm-lever-belt-black?aff=172\">The belt</a> is equipped with an adjustable matte black lever buckle, which can be programmed to fit your support needs. Smooth edges, reinforced stitching, and interior suede liner bring ultimate comfort during workouts of different intensities.</p><p>This belt is comfortable, durable, and reliable when performing squats, bench presses, deadlifts, and other compound movements. It is marketed to withstand serious powerlifting sessions and perfect for lifting heavy weights, as it was tested under tough conditions working out with the barbell.</p><p>The belt comes with reinforced double stitching to improve its durability and has a suede lining that not only makes it comfortable to wear but also protects the leather from sweat.</p>",
            "product_review_image": "shopify://shop_images/training-lever-belt-gymreapers-insta.jpg",
            "half_width_review_image": true,
            "product_review_image_caption": "<p>Photo by <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/C0wumwhgNNF/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link&igsh=MzRlODBiNWFlZA==\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/C0wumwhgNNF/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link&igsh=MzRlODBiNWFlZA==\">@_freddykano_</a></p>",
            "product_text_content_2": "<p>The combination of high-quality leather and an easy-to-use matte black buckle will bring you optimal support for your core during tough lifts. With a single flick of the lever, you can control the tightness of the belt without struggling with traditional buckles and prongs.</p><p>You not only save time but also can choose a more personalized fit for better security and comfort. As a result, you can focus on your workout without distractions or discomfort.</p><p>Gymreapers belt better suits short and intense drills. It's designed with a function to quickly tighten the belt to the max to perform compound lifts and intense reps and quickly loosen it for normal breathing and movement.</p><p>The 10mm belt is slightly thinner, offering greater mobility and flexibility while being fully tightened on the body. The 4” width offers better support; however, it won't fit lifters with short torsos. You can benefit from using this belt for deadlifts as it offers all the support you may need for a long time.</p>",
            "product_pros": "<ul><li>Designed for short, intense stints of use</li><li>Marketed as a USPA-approved belt</li><li>There is a short breaking-in period due to the thickness of the belt</li><li>Features a strong lever that doesn’t pop open unexpectedly</li></ul>",
            "product_cons": "<ul><li>Not a full 4” — it’s 3.75” wide, so it may feel stiff in the rib area</li><li>The bolts provided for the lever are too short to get proper thread engagement</li></ul>"
          }
