            "product_text_content_1": "<p>Titan company's policy is that everyone should use premium products without overpaying it to help achieve your goals. That’s why the brand aims to preserve two things: build reliable fitness equipment that withstands intense workouts and provide realistically priced equipment that is affordable for everyone.</p><p>The belt comes with seven holes located 1\" apart, which you can adjust with the help of a screwdriver to move the lever up or down to fit your waist size.</p><p>Thanks to the clean design and secure fit, this <a href=\"https://titan-fitness.pxf.io/750oOr\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://titan-fitness.pxf.io/750oOr\">lever belt</a> is built to last while <a href=\"https://blog.warmbody-coldmind.com/guides/do-you-need-a-belt-to-deadlift/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://blog.warmbody-coldmind.com/guides/do-you-need-a-belt-to-deadlift/\">performing deadlifts</a>, squats, and bent-over rows. To benefit from wearing this lifting accessory, the manufacturer offers to measure in-between sizes and choose the smaller option.</p><p>This belt will suit best powerlifters, strongmen, and any strength-training-oriented devotees. Lifters aiming to enhance their core strength while reducing the risk of lower back injuries will benefit from wearing this lever belt.</p><p>The intermediate and advanced lifters who want to move their performance to the next level can also find this accessory useful. Specifically, they will appreciate its functionality, as they'll learn to perform the movements correctly.</p><p>The key purpose of this lever belt is to create intra-abdominal pressure to stabilize the core during heavy lifts. Additionally, it enhances support for performance, provides quick and secure fastening, and vouches for customizable fit to any lifter.</p>",
